&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Director / VP Sales will be responsible for executing a consultative sale to Fortune 1000 brand, shopper, and media agency teams. The ideal candidate is a creator marketing and influencer expert (strong digital, social background), be a hunter, solution based seller and results oriented.&amp;nbsp; You should have established client relationships in the CPG, QSR, finance, or healthcare / pharma verticals. You will own the entire sales cycle and be responsible for prospecting, understanding the customer&#39;s needs and presenting solutions as a trusted partner.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
