&lt;li&gt;Apply a consultative sales approach that focuses on client objectives, but also maintain a sense of urgency on closing deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have the ability to convey our solution with passion with a focus on the value of targeted, trend forward , creator&amp;nbsp; generated content at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand the value of data driven media solutions and be able to leverage insights and analytics to penetrate clients and close deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strategic client relationships through large ($1M+) annual and multi-year contractual commitments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive open opportunities to close in quarter with an eye towards building a strong pipeline for subsequent quarters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a book of business from the ground-up, mentor team members, and prepare for additional leadership as we scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help develop and refine our in-market partner approach by becoming a lead story teller and educate our clients on our platform’s best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply creativity, demonstrate accountability and maintain a deep understanding of Linqia’s services and business model&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a highly dynamic environment with a proven ability to balance competing demands and priorities as well as operate independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively manage a rapidly growing sales pipeline/channel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be comfortable with carrying a Sales quota,&amp;nbsp; be accountable for delivering revenue, and expect to be handsomely rewarded for over achieving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;+7 years of proven success selling in digital sales and/or online media to executive-level brand clients / agency partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Established and transferable relationships in CPG, restaurant, apparel or entertainment verticals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of consistent quota achievement above goal - we&#39;re looking for all-stars!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable experience closing committed deals in excess of $1M annually&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong consultative sales

